cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of machine learning and deep learning techniques for medical image analysis, specifically for Alzheimer's Disease diagnostics. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of fusion of imaging modalities, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper uses data from the Alzheimer's Disease Neuroimaging Initiative (ADNI) dataset, which is a common dataset in medical imaging (cs.MM) research.
